--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Database
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  - MariaDB Server (GPL-2.0-only) https://mariadb.org/

MariaDB Server is bundled in the compose stack as a separate container. The
application communicates with it over the standard MySQL/MariaDB wire
protocol via the PyMySQL client library (MIT). MariaDB Server source is
available from https://mariadb.org/download/.

